title: Peeps Flavored Oreos Are Now A Thing! | Mojo in the Morning | Channel 955
text:
Peeps Flavored Oreos Are Now A Thing! posted by Joey - â€” Mojo In The Morning (@MojoInTheMorn) February 20, 2017 
There were rumors a few months ago that Peeps flavored Oreo's were in the works. The Internet exploded with commentary on the Easter treat making its transition to the popular cream-filled cookie. Let's just say, people were skeptical. 
Now it's official... the Peeps Oreo are here! For now, you can find them at a Walmart store near you. They'll soon be available everywhere. Wake up with us every morning starting at 5am on Detroit's #1 Hit Music Station, Channel 955! Contact
